## All content used in JCP paper

--> numerical_simulations
    Reference and PinT simulations of the Gaussian bumps and unstable jet test cases

--> stability_regions
    Analytical stability study

--> test_mpi_openmp
    Preliminary tests of hybrid MPI-OpenMP parallelization

--> Tikz_figures
    Produces figures using Tikz

--> viscosity_coefficients
    Overview on viscosity theory

